short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that manages tabs and groups them by domain.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabManager is a powerful Chrome extension designed to help you manage and organize your browser tabs with ease. Whether you're dealing with a large number of open tabs or want to group them by domain or window, TabManager has you covered.
